T(n)\ge G\iff (1+C)^{n-1}A\ge G\iff(1+C)^{n-1}\ge\frac{G}{A}\iff n\ge\log_{1+C}\frac GA+1,
T(n)\lt G\iff n\lt \log_{1+C}\frac{G}{A}+1.
